snippet.textDisplay:
The WHO agreed the next step is to investigate the trade of live badgers, rabbits and bats.
Cosmetic scientists should be redeployed to research the three species and their changing environment.
Climatic changes, food chains, dietary changes and common sense is required.
Toitu te marae a Tane-Mahuta, Toitu te marae a Tangaroa, Toitu te tangata. If the land is well and the sea is well, the people will thrive.
